episodes.title: My Life After the Netflix Documentary of 7m Tiktok Cult
episodes.description:
This is my journey after the Netflix docuseries Dancing for the Devil: The 7M Tiktok cult. 
I was part of this cult for 23 years and now I want to create awareness for everyone who can relate to my story.
